You can also control sides individually:
margin-top: 10px;
margin-right: 20px;
margin-bottom: 10px;
margin-left: 20px;

margin: 20px;              /* all sides */
margin: 10px 30px;         /* top-bottom | left-right */
margin: 10px 20px 30px 40px; /* top | right | bottom | left */

Difference

| Property | Space Location | Use Case                         |
| -------- | -------------- | -------------------------------- |
| Padding  | Inside border  | Increase space around content    |
| Margin   | Outside border | Create distance between elements |

